creator: TRAVELLINE
descriptionHtml:
TravelLine extranet on your Android device. Check on your reservations and manage them from any place with Internet. All changes are fully synchronized with the web version of TravelLine extranet.

All users of TravelLine extranet will find this app handy.

Functions
Reservations management:
· Calendar with past and future reservations.
· Reservation details.
· Filtering by reservation type.
· Cancellation rules.

Rooms availability management:
· Quota blocks management.
· Collecting availability details by all accommodation categories.
· Setting availability parameters for selected dates.
· Long-term group setting of availability.
· Stop of sales.

News feed:
· Notifications about reservations.
· Daily report on the number of reservations and arrivals.

Rates management:
· Room rates modifications.
· Long-term rates setting.
· Setting rates in a group operation for a selected period.
descriptionShort: Mobile extranet always at hand for TravelLine clients.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml: Thank you for using TL Extranet. We regularly issue updates to make our app even better for you. Each update of TL Extranet contains improvements for its response time and reliability.
